["desc"] = "Fully Customizable Clock & Date\n-------------------------------------------\n* Group with 3 Children\n* Individually re-positionable \"Clock\", \"Date\" and \"Clock Label\" (which displays the text \"Local Time\" or \"Realm Time\")\n* Use the WeakAuras \"Display\" tab to adjust the Font, Font Size, Text Color, Opacity, Outline and Shadow Color for each individual child\n* Use the WeakAuras Group's \"Custom Options\" tab to adjust the format(s) in which the \"Clock\" and \"Date\" display\n----------\nThrottle\n----------\n* In order to not process the code on \"Every Frame\", I have added a \"Throttle\" \"if\" statement to the \"Trigger 2\" \"Custom Trigger\" code on the \"Clock\" and \"Date\" children. This throttle runs the \"Clock\" and \"Date\" children's \"Display\" \"%c\" custom code every 0.5 seconds.\n------\nBugs\n------\n* If you notice any bugs, kindly leave them in the Comments section on wago.io and I will try to fix them\n* I found a bug that disabled the Clock's time at midnight on \"12-Hour\" Format, \"Realm Time.\" I believe I fixed this issue.",
